{"id": "486de1a3603ccf08dfc75b8d0aa4079e92627138f8b54f0e5eb039addb770b72", "item_id": "4f9ab4a92b:0", "text": "Inverts one or more components of the incoming color. The input color can be in the in the RGB, HSL, or HSV color models. Note: The output is a RGB color clamped to the"}
{"id": "663ea1bfffe5038f3f0cf667f14c4257eff52d77ce7f2a218f72e9286616ea39", "item_id": "4f9ab4a92b:1", "text": "to"}
{"id": "5b450b391a66050b7a2b33ba81cd8e5099a373831bc01c2d021ee3242f307c5a", "item_id": "4f9ab4a92b:2", "text": "range."}
{"id": "a0fbb0152c545070cb1163ff7badbf178ac79418a41c83336fd75e19844dc148", "item_id": "4f9ab4a92b:5", "text": "The color that you would like to invert."}
{"id": "8533fc1ad96dc818bd731e6f0a322fedf20b5d47169c49e61e25fff428f871b0", "item_id": "4f9ab4a92b:6", "text": "Color Model"}
{"id": "53a5e0a5df3438ae514ff7a6ca80f528ea25981f13120c3b1273e29f343b28ed", "item_id": "4f9ab4a92b:7", "text": "The inputColor uses this color model."}
{"id": "c9eac5388f3cc6bc6e3b72266689adc0a2ba55897ed2a123c7c9f79fb6170c0e", "item_id": "4f9ab4a92b:8", "text": "0: RGB"}
{"id": "2802eef0cfe483a8e3e54273a9249d76f2ac4cf0be0473f0a635c1deafc5d675", "item_id": "4f9ab4a92b:9", "text": "1: HSL"}
{"id": "fb8ee2cc5bcca6ce1164ae418e2dd58cf05c6583d80dfae841a7af4e7b2fa954", "item_id": "4f9ab4a92b:10", "text": "2: HSV"}
{"id": "aa961b6b52c85867b3a6262d347e97c7da433d6f6dd3956750b659c2dd97db6f", "item_id": "4f9ab4a92b:11", "text": "Invert Channel 0"}
{"id": "4903e5bcb5a0c711efef8485aa1183ccb32923e089c9e343cfba61d62e9d2cc0", "item_id": "4f9ab4a92b:12", "text": "When enabled (set to 1) the first color channel is inverted. For example, if the color model is set to RGB, then the R channel will be inverted."}
{"id": "f0ff9e8d5b255b45cce0f9b199d86779c14c66dda5b7066dd1a41336d4aecb7e", "item_id": "4f9ab4a92b:13", "text": "Invert Channel 1"}
{"id": "34205b1d3219a836a9579ceb9d1ba618393d6cc455d7a713a74aa974948dc86f", "item_id": "4f9ab4a92b:14", "text": "When enabled (set to 1) the second color channel is inverted. For example, if the color model is set to RGB, then the G channel will be inverted."}
{"id": "ef2f73b7b020a174dce981a99fd76940c201128c9ae02ab67ac432e89cb33daf", "item_id": "4f9ab4a92b:15", "text": "Invert Channel 2"}
{"id": "ce4cfbf07e65ef7c6c7f6a1afe989d032c030835dc004fdad555e014fe28195a", "item_id": "4f9ab4a92b:16", "text": "When enabled (set to 1) the third color channel is inverted. For example, if the color model is set to RGB, then the B channel will be inverted."}
